Embraer Legacy 450/500 and Praetor 500/600 MENUS AND DISPLAYS Pro Line Fusion® Avionics Chart – Chart Task Menu

Airspace Airspace is a submenu select button to access the airspace chart submenu for the associated airport.

Previous Menu Previous Menu is a button to return to the previous Chart menu (Origin, Destination, Alternate, or Other).
